[[File:Library_Busts_AotC.png|thumb|right|250px|The Jedi library on Coruscant]]
A '''Jedi library''' was a database containing information relating to the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] and its history. Jedi libraries were administered by [[Jedi librarian/Legends|Jedi librarians]] (such as [[Atris]], and [[Jocasta Nu/Legends|Jocasta Nu]]) and accessible only to members of the Jedi Order. Some were even restricted to members of having certain ranks, such as [[Dorak]]'s library in the [[Jedi Enclave]] on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]], which was reserved for [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] only.

Perhaps the greatest Jedi libraries in the history of the Order was [[Odan-Urr/Legends|Odan-Urr's]] [[Great Jedi Library/Legends|Great Jedi Library]] on Ossus, which was founded around [[5000 BBY/Legends|5000 BBY]] and destroyed around [[4000 BBY/Legends|4000 BBY]], the one on [[Exis Station/Legends|Exis Station]] and the [[Jedi Archives/Legends|Jedi Archives]] in the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], administered by Jocasta Nu around the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

